div1.p:
Cole. The old one (
Ann Ellard
) was in Bed, but I cannot say whether my Fellow-Apprentice was, they were in the House at ten o'Clock, and soon after that I went to sleep; I cannot tell how long they staid afterwards.

Gyles. Those who are Judges took it to be about three Months old;
Robert Hobbins
is the Night-Man, who took the Child up.
